WEBVTT

NOTE: Estimated from known TTS script; timing requires human review before Tier 1 captions.

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:10.066
If you need to sell your house fast in Concord, New Hampshire, USA Home Buyers can help you move forward without repairs, showings, or agent fees.

2
00:00:10.066 --> 00:00:18.583
We buy houses as-is throughout Concord and Merrimack County, including Penacook, East Concord, West Concord, and the South End / Downtown area.

3
00:00:18.583 --> 00:00:21.083
Maybe the property needs work.

4
00:00:21.083 --> 00:00:30.374
Maybe you inherited it, have tenants in place, are behind on payments, or just want a clean sale without waiting on a retail buyer.

5
00:00:30.374 --> 00:00:37.343
You do not have to clean it out, update it, or make it perfect before we can talk.

6
00:00:37.343 --> 00:00:39.843
Here is how the process works.

7
00:00:39.843 --> 00:00:46.811
You tell us about the house, we review the property, and we give you a written cash offer.

8
00:00:46.811 --> 00:00:51.070
If the offer works for you, you choose the closing date.

9
00:00:51.070 --> 00:00:57.651
We can often close quickly, but we also work around your timeline when you need more time.

10
00:00:57.651 --> 00:01:01.136
There is no obligation, no pressure, and no commission.

11
00:01:01.136 --> 00:01:08.491
We also explain the offer clearly so you are not guessing about fees, timing, or what happens after closing.

12
00:01:08.491 --> 00:01:15.073
If you want a straightforward cash offer for a Concord-area home, call USA Home Buyers at 888-274-5006.

13
00:01:15.073 --> 00:01:21.300
We will walk you through the next step and help you decide if a cash sale makes sense.
